      <title>俄罗斯法令缓解担忧，欧洲天然气价格继续下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/european-gas-extends-losses-with-russian-decree-easing-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫改变了支付俄罗斯天然气的程序，缓解了人们对该地区天然气供应将被切断的担忧，导致欧洲天然气价格本周延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/european-gas-extends-losses-with-russian-decree-easing-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:59:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 暂停减产引发银行低调回应，市场担忧仍未消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/opec-pause-earns-low-key-response-from-banks-as-concerns-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银行和行业顾问表示，OPEC+将恢复供应的时间推迟至4月份，此举将削减明年全球石油产量，在一定程度上收紧供应平衡，但人们普遍预计仍将出现供过于求的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/opec-pause-earns-low-key-response-from-banks-as-concerns-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:52:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里：OPEC+决策是最现实的最佳结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/hari-opec-decision-is-most-realistic-optimum-outcome-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+ 已同意再次将恢复石油生产的时间推迟三个月。VANDA Insights 创始人 Vandana Hari 接受了彭博社《中东和非洲视野》节目主持人 Joumanna Bercetche 的采访，并解释说，OPEC+ 的决定并没有给石油市场带来冲击，因为此举只是减少了供应过剩。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/hari-opec-decision-is-most-realistic-optimum-outcome-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:31:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价两年来涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/uk-house-prices-jump-1-3-to-record-high-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国一家最大的抵押贷款机构表示，由于预算不确定性结束、降息和低失业率刺激了购房需求，英国房价出现两年多来最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/uk-house-prices-jump-1-3-to-record-high-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工业生产下滑导致德国经济衰退风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/german-industrial-production-unexpectedly-declined-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国工业生产 10 月份出现下滑，拉开了最后一个季度的序幕，出现意外下滑，粉碎了人们对欧洲最大经济体这一关键行业可能正在缓慢摆脱困境的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/german-industrial-production-unexpectedly-declined-in-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
