    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 再次选择推迟恢复产量计划，油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+ 决定将停产生产的恢复时间再推迟三个月，但未能提振市场人气，预计明年将出现供应过剩，油价因此企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 23:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Aviva 达成 36 亿英镑收购 Direct Line 的初步协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/aviva-said-to-near-preliminary-deal-with-direct-line-after-bump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国汽车保险公司 Aviva Plc 就收购 Direct Line Insurance Group Plc 的条款达成了初步协议，在数月的抵制收购兴趣之后，这家公司最终屈服于追求者的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/aviva-said-to-near-preliminary-deal-with-direct-line-after-bump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 22:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
